    <!-- DSA Info Modal -->
    <div class="modal" id="dsaModal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
        <div class="modal-content" style="max-width: 600px;">
            <h2>üéØ Data Structures & Algorithms Used</h2>
            <div style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 13px;">
                <p><strong style="color: var(--primary);">1. Doubly Linked List</strong><br>
                - Playlists implemented as doubly linked lists<br>
                - O(1) next/previous navigation<br>
                - Efficient insertion/deletion</p>
                
                <p><strong style="color: var(--primary);">2. Stack (LIFO)</strong><br>
                - Recently Played uses stack<br>
                - Push new songs, pop when limit reached<br>
                - O(1) operations</p>
                
                <p><strong style="color: var(--primary);">3. Hash Map</strong><br>
                - Playlists stored in HashMap<br>
                - O(1) lookup by name<br>
                - Fast access to any playlist</p>
                
                <p><strong style="color: var(--primary);">4. Fisher-Yates Shuffle</strong><br>
                - True random shuffle algorithm<br>
                - O(n) time complexity<br>
                - Unbiased randomization</p>
                
                <p><strong style="color: var(--primary);">5. Merge Sort</strong><br>
                - Stable sorting algorithm<br>
                - O(n log n) guaranteed<br>
                - Used for name/artist sorting</p>
                
                <p><strong style="color: var(--primary);">6. Quick Sort</strong><br>
                - O(n log n) average case<br>
                - Used for duration sorting<br>
                - Divide and conquer</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-buttons" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <button class="modal-btn cancel" onclick="closeDSAModal()" style="width: 100%;">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

